features: ✅Easy to Clean & Dishwasher Safe - Cleaning up is a breeze with Creativ Collective's reusable silicone air fryer liners. Not only are they 100% dishwasher safe, they also help protect your air fryer from grease, food residue, and grime. The foldable design helps for saving space when storing the silicone liner in your drawer or cabinet.

✅Eco-Friendly and Saves Money - Our reusable air fryer liners are a great substitute for the disposable air fryer liners. A one-time investment for all of your cooking needs. Save your money and protect our environment with these collapsible air fryer silicone pot!

✅Improved Heavy-Duty Design - Most air fryer silicone liners are thin and flimsy. Not ours! Our square air fryer liners are designed with a large carrying capacity and double the thickness. The thicker handles provide a much easier grip for transportation. They are the perfect gift for cooking lovers, family, and friends.

✅100% Heat-Resistant and Food-Safe Material - Our premium silicone air fryer liners are made of food-grade BPA-Free silicone that is oil-proof, non-stick, non-toxic, and heat resistant. They can withstand temperatures up to 450 degrees and are perfect for your air fryer, oven, microwave, steamers, and crockpot.

✅Unique Oil Guide Groove Design - Our durable air fryer silicone pots have raised grooves at the bottom that helps separate the grease and other residue from your food. The silicone air fryer basket also improves air circulation for an even heat distribution while cooking your food.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good thickness, foldable, and black . . .
reviews.reviewText: These silicone airfryer liners are a good thickness and can be folded for easy storage. I also wanted a color that would not stain as they are black and also come with a handy silicone coated tongs. Sometimes there are some items that are a bit messy when cooking and these come in handy to make it easier to clean basket. Excellent.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient and durable.
reviews.reviewText: CONVENIENT, CONVENIENT, CONVENIENT! My wife is absolutely in love with it. The fact that we’re not getting our air fryer tray dirty is great, but this thing is collapsible and fits a lot of food. Talk about easy to clean too. I was even able to throw it in my smoker and make a smoked queso. I was expecting the smoke flavor to penetrate the silicone but nope, you’d never know it once you reuse it again in the air fryer. I’ll definitely be buying more of these. 10 out of 10 for sure.
